&lt;p&gt;The Director of Membership Growth &amp;amp; Engagement is responsible for driving membership growth, engagement, and retention through innovative, data-informed strategies. Partnering with the Vice President of Membership &amp;amp; Components, this role leads long-term planning, recruitment initiatives, and efforts to strengthen the member value proposition.&lt;/p&gt;
